{
  "stem": "54.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That we should get ready, they taking us out from the house, and away from work, and they're going to send us to another place where we're going to have work, we're going to eat, and it's going to be good for us and everything.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were so naive, we believe them, that this is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But unfortunate, didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took-- so they accumulate probably about few hundred people in the police station, and then, from the police station, they send us-- they took us, again, on the trains.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That time, we didn't know where we going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- and the trains were not like passenger trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was trains, you know, where they were-- you know, transport-- transport train, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "With no windows, only a door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They put us in like bunch of animals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They closed the doors, they sealed the doors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we going back and forth, back and forth for a few-- for a few-- maybe a week, to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't know it was Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were like the sheeps there, going, everywhere they just told us to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We came in, in a place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We walked down, you know, with the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We came-- we come there, and we see that a lot of machines, sewing machines are on the-- are on the lot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were start-- you know, laughing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, we're going to work here like they told us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, but unfortunate, it was not like they told us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right away, when I came to Auschwitz, then it was, this is Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then when I came with my father, I went left, and my father went right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since then, I didn't see him anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the camp Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
